oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Willie Nelson at Enmax Centre
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Metal photoplates; Nelson, Willie, 1933-; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (black and red on yellow) announcing an evening with Willie Nelson (singer, songwriter, actor, and author) at the Enmax Centre on July 17. Poster features a metal photoplate of Willie Nelson and woodcuts of maple leaves. Poster is a limited edition of 150.
